    "redesign_intro": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "Redesign intro",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width page-width--narrow\" style=\"padding:1rem 0 3rem; text-align:left;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:1.6rem; line-height:1.7;\">San Francisco is home. I've designed and redesigned fine jewelry here since 2002 — resetting diamonds, reimagining heirlooms, and turning gold people no longer wear into pieces they reach for every day. Wherever you are in the city, you can work with me directly, in person or entirely remotely.</p>\n  <h2>What I redesign for San Francisco clients</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"/pages/reset-diamond-ring\">Diamond &amp; gemstone resetting</a> — move your stones into a setting made for you today.</li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pages/redesign-engagement-ring\">Engagement ring redesign</a> — reimagine your ring using your own diamond and gold.</li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pages/heirloom-jewelry-redesign\">Heirloom &amp; inherited jewelry redesign</a> — honor the piece, make it wearable again.</li>\n    <li><a href=\"/pages/use-your-own-gems-metal\">Use your own gold &amp; stones</a> — I refine your gold and reset your stones.</li>\n    <li>Custom design and turning rings into necklaces &amp; pendants.</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2>Where can I get my diamond reset in San Francisco?</h2>\n  <p>Right here. I reset diamonds and gemstones for clients across Pacific Heights, Presidio Heights, Noe Valley, Cole Valley, the Marina, Russian Hill, and St. Francis Wood. You can meet with me in person or send your stones fully insured and tracked — your jewelry is documented at every step.</p>\n  <h2>Who does heirloom jewelry redesign in San Francisco?</h2>\n  <p>As a solo designer, I personally handle every San Francisco redesign from first sketch to finished piece — no factory, no outsourcing, and your heirloom never leaves one pair of hands.</p>\n  <h2>How much does jewelry redesign cost in San Francisco?</h2>\n  <p>Every redesign is custom, and because you supply your own gold and stones it usually costs less than buying new. You get a transparent quote after a free consultation. <a href=\"/pages/jewelry-redesign-cost\">See the full pricing guide →</a></p>\n  <h2>Can I redesign my jewelry remotely from San Francisco?</h2>\n  <p>Yes. The entire process — consultation, design, approval, and delivery — can be done remotely with insured, tracked shipping, so you never have to set foot in a store if you'd rather not.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top:2.5rem;\"><a href=\"/pages/contact\" class=\"button\">Book your free consultation</a></p>\n</div>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 24,
        "padding_bottom": 12
      }
    },
